{"tid":838543,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【不再一年不腐】麥當勞「走」防腐劑 7款包成功 但其餘未得","createTime":"2018-09-27T07:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T02:50:30.000Z","uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1debb7c608ea43a79766e2c27def0c2ccb68d1","tid":838543,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"記得有營養學家示範麥當勞開心樂園餐可放一年不腐爛嗎？這情況或者慢慢成為歷史，麥當勞為改變形象改良食譜多年。麥當勞周三表示，目前美國的「巨無霸」及「芝士足三両」已經可以不含防腐劑。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞稱，改良了麵包及醬汁後，「巨無霸」及「芝士足三両」等7款包全部不含防腐劑，不過醃青瓜仍含有人工防腐劑，消費者可以要求不要醃青瓜。<br />\n<br />\n近年消費者更注重健康，麥當勞亦逐漸改變，包括2016年不會再在包類食品中使用會上癮及加劇癡肥的「高果糖玉米糖漿」（HFCS），同時在麥樂雞內停用人工防腐劑。<br />\n<br />\n目前餐廳內仍有三分一包類含有人造色素、添加劑或防腐劑，包括煙肉蛋漢堡與魚柳包，麥當勞未有就移除這些人工添加劑設定詳細時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180927/58728659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728659&d=ponsyYfsuH7%2BR%2BoRpLuOk5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6a324d8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728659&h=e9672099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180927/58728659</a>"},{"pid":"f9ca84318c98150dad0e98005e096a25fbebc8c3","tid":838543,"uid":136186,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"要健康就咪食m記啦"},{"pid":"c1fc92d699c71e7b8e770862f49f5bf2395e998a","tid":838543,"uid":72608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9ca84318c98150dad0e98005e096a25fbebc8c3","tid":838543,"uid":136186,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"要健康就咪食m記啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"要健康就留係屋企啦"},{"pid":"ddeb750b1967f9e2135589d7ec3ae5185514b7fd","tid":838543,"uid":44454,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"冇防腐劑我食嚟把撚呀"},{"pid":"c